import React from 'react' import "./reserve.css" import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome' import { faCircleXmark } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons' import useFetch from '../../hooks/useFetch' const Reserve = ({ setOpen, hoteId }) => { const { data, loading, error } = useFetch(`hotels/rooms/${hoteId}`) return (
setOpen(false)} /> Select Your rooms: {data.map(item => (
{item.title}
{item.desc}
Max People: {item.maxPeople}
))}
) } export default Reserve
